> Will I run into problems rewiring a 12volt convert with a '65 harness or 
> should I get something along the lines of a '67 harness ???

Hi Doug,
The wiring harness will work fine, but you will need to put a voltage reducer 
before the wiper or burn it out all too quickly.  Of course you will need to 
replace ALL light bulbs including interior ones before melting a nice OG 
lense.
Eric&Barb
